… и локальные семинары",is_note:b,text_block:"\u003Cp\u003EЧерез пару месяцев после Digitale, я увидел информацию о семинаре Serenity, где специалисты агентства делятся знаниями. От конференции впечатления были только хорошие, поэтому семинар выглядел отличной идеей и таковым оказался.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n",note_counter:a,note:a,expert:b}]},{acf_fc_layout:S,type:as,photos:[{ID:asl,id:asl,title:"h5cmHDb7x2U",filename:"h5cmHDb7x2U.jpg",url:yN,alt:a,author:u,description:a,caption:a,name:"h5cmhdb7x2u",date:"2019-04-30 15:23:57",modified:asm,mime_type:K,type:v,icon:w,width:Q,height:Y,sizes:{thumbnail:"https:\u002F\u002Fserenity.agency\u002Fadmin\u002Fwp-content\u002Fuploads\u002F2019\u002F04\u002Fh5cmHDb7x2U-300x300.jpg","thumbnail-width":h,"thumbnail-height":h,medium:asn,"medium-width":k,"medium-height":i,medium_large:"https:\u002F\u002Fserenity.agency\u002Fadmin\u002Fwp-content\u002Fuploads\u002F2019\u002F04\u002Fh5cmHDb7x2U-768x512.jpg","medium_large-width":z,"medium_large-height":bz,large:yN,"large-width":Q,"large-height":Y,carousel:"https:\u002F\u002Fserenity.agency\u002Fadmin\u002Fwp-content\u002Fuploads\u002F2019\u002F04\u002Fh5cmHDb7x2U-750x500.jpg","carousel-width":B,"carousel-height":l,wide:"https:\u002F\u002Fserenity.agency\u002Fadmin\u002Fwp-content\u002Fuploads\u002F2019\u002F04\u002Fh5cmHDb7x2U-1280x500.jpg","wide-width":Q,"wide-height":l,standart:"https:\u002F\u002Fserenity.agency\u002Fadmin\u002Fwp-content\u002Fuploads\u002F2019\u002F04\u002Fh5cmHDb7x2U-1200x800.jpg","standart-width":F,"standart-height":al,"thumb-x2":"https:\u002F\u002Fserenity.agency\u002Fadmin\u002Fwp-content\u002Fuploads\u002F2019\u002F04\u002Fh5cmHDb7x2U-600x600.jpg","thumb-x2-width":i,"thumb-x2-height":i,case:"https:\u002F\u002Fserenity.agency\u002Fadmin\u002Fwp-content\u002Fuploads\u002F2019\u002F04\u002Fh5cmHDb7x2U-450x300.jpg","case-width":y,"case-height":h,case2x:asn,"case2x-width":k,"case2x-height":i,caseBig:"https:\u002F\u002Fserenity.agency\u002Fadmin\u002Fwp-content\u002Fuplo